---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="OpenClaw 一键部署方案对比">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="flex gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">#OpenClaw</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-full">#Docker</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">OpenClaw 一键部署方案对比</h1>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <time>2026-03-18</time>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">🤔 在思考</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900">背景</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">需要为团队快速部署 OpenClaw 飞书机器人，调研了两个方案。</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900">方案一：Tauri 图形安装器 (推荐)</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">基于 <code>openclawapp</code> 项目定制。</p>
      
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3 text-gray-900">优点</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>✅ 成功率 90%+</li>
        <li>✅ 体积小 (100MB)</li>
        <li>✅ 用户体验好，傻瓜式操作</li>
        <li>✅ 跨平台 (Windows/macOS/Linux)</li>
        <li>✅ 维护成本低</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900">方案二：Docker 一键安装包</h2>
      
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3 text-gray-900">缺点</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>❌ 成功率仅 30-40%</li>
        <li>❌ 体积巨大 (2GB+)</li>
        <li>❌ 依赖 Docker Desktop，安装复杂</li>
        <li>❌ Windows 家庭版/WSL2 兼容性问题</li>
        <li>❌ 资源占用高 (8GB 内存)</li>
        <li>❌ 维护成本极高</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900">GLM-5 锐评</h2>
      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 italic text-gray-600 mb-6">
        "方案二是典型的技术自嗨：用大炮打蚊子，还打歪了。投入产出比为负。不要做。用方案一。Period."
      </blockquote>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900">结论</h2>
      <p class="mb-4"><strong>采用方案一 (Tauri 图形安装器)</strong></p>
      <p>理由：成功率更高、用户体验更好、维护成本更低、已有成熟方案可用。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <a href="/ideas" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600">← 返回想法流</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
